ather, father, grandmother, and aunt, highlighting its destructive potential. The bloodline is both a blessing and a curse, as it enhances physical prowess but simultaneously erodes the bearer's body, posing a constant threat of death. 阿苏勒's father, aware of the dangers, hoped that his son could learn to control and suppress this volatile force. Despite its risks, \"青铜之血\" remains a defining tradition of the 帕苏尔 family, though its survival now faces significant challenges. This dual nature of immense power and inherent peril makes \"青铜之血\" a central and complex element of the 帕苏尔 legacy.", "青铜重鼎:青铜重鼎是白胤下令铸造的，安置在北固山城堡，七百年未动，象征防御和力量"], "parameters": {"model": "text-embedding-v3"}}}